s the benefit of further alterations in lipid levels is anticipated to outweigh the potential risks.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/166099/', '', 'Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Simvastatin, Dextrothyroxine, Probucol, Colesevelam, Alirocumab', 'Guar gum, Pramlintide, Alogliptin, Empagliflozin, Dulaglutide, Exenatide, Miglitol, Albiglutide, Rosiglitazone, Ertugliflozin, Semaglutide, More', 1767369485);
