thromycin is considered contraindicated.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/166161/', '', 'Glipizide, Acetohexamide, Guar gum, Pramlintide, Alogliptin, Tolazamide, Empagliflozin, Dulaglutide, Exenatide, Tolbutamide, Miglitol, More', 'Dirithromycin', 1767369485);
